OL,3,CCricketer picked for T20 World Cup
OL,4,Cdespite guilty court plea
OL,6,FJersey Cricket has selected Nick
OL,7,FGreenwood for its upcoming T20 World
OL,8,FCup Qualifiers squad, despite him
OL,9,Fpleading guilty to three driving
OL,10,Foffences.
OL,12,FThe 25-year-old is one of the island's
OL,13,Fleading batsmen, scoring 936 runs
OL,14,Fduring 34 T20 appearances for the
OL,15,FBailiwick since his debut in 2019.
OL,17,FHe is one of two full-time
OL,18,Fprofessionals in Jersey's 15-man team
OL,19,Fand regularly travels over for matches
OL,20,Ffrom his home in New Zealand, where he
OL,21,Fplays for Wellington.
