OL,3,CCricketer picked for T20 World Cup
OL,4,Cdespite guilty court plea
OL,6,FGreenwood was instrumental in this
OL,7,Fmonth's inter-insular win over
OL,8,FGuernsey.
OL,10,FHowever, following post-match
OL,11,Fcelebrations in Jersey, the island's
OL,12,FMagistrate's Court heard he got behind
OL,13,Fthe wheel and drove the wrong way down
OL,14,Fa one-way road without any headlights
OL,15,Fon.
OL,17,FGreenwood was spotted by another
OL,18,Fdriver who reported it to the police
OL,19,Fand officers found his car parked at
OL,20,Fan address.
