OL,3,CCricketer picked for T20 World Cup
OL,4,Cdespite guilty court plea
OL,6,FThe Court heard that Greenwood was
OL,7,Fslurring his words, unsteady on his
OL,8,Ffeet and then fell down the stairs.
OL,10,FPolice asked him to carry out a drink-
OL,11,Fdrive test, but he failed multiple
OL,12,Ftimes to provide a sample.
OL,14,FGreenwood pleaded guilty to driving
OL,15,Fwithout insurance, failing to provide
OL,16,Fa specimen for analysis, and failing
OL,17,Fto comply with traffic directions
OL,18,Fduring the court hearing on Tuesday.
OL,20,FHe is set to return to court in late
OL,21,FJuly when he will be sentenced.
