OL,6,FIn response to Greenwood's selection,
OL,7,Fthe Chief Executive Officer of Jersey
OL,8,FCricket, Sarah Gomersall, says: "We
OL,9,Facknowledge the seriousness of the
OL,10,Fsituation and are disappointed that it
OL,11,Fhas arisen.
OL,13,F"However, with legal proceedings
OL,14,Fongoing, we are not in a position to
OL,15,Fcomment further at this stage."
