OL,6,FJersey Cricket adds that it is not
OL,7,Ffunding any of Greenwood's legal costs
OL,8,Fand his selection follows a precedent
OL,9,Fset by other international teams such
OL,10,Fas New Zealand and England, where
OL,11,Fplayers facing non-cricket-related
OL,12,Flegal proceedings can continue to
OL,13,Frepresent their teams on sporting
OL,14,Fmerit alone.
